        Her husband Mr Behl told reporters that "the disease can come back" even though the treatment has ended. Irrfan Khan: Bollywood actor flooded with support after cancer letter
Bollywood challenges India's mental health taboo
After her diagnosis, Bendre took to Instagram with a post in which she said she "was determined to fight" the cancer and thanked her family and friends. She added that her "high-grade cancer" had metastised.Fans flocked to the comments section, wishing her the best for a speedy recovery. 
    
        
